// Coin Transaction Endpoints

### Get All Coin Transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions

### Get Coin Transaction by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions/1

### Get Coin Transaction (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions/99999

### Get Coin Transaction (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions/invalid

### Get Player Coin Transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/coin-transactions

### Get Player Coin Transactions (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/coin-transactions

### Create Coin Transaction
POST http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1,
  "amount": 500,
  "type": "listing_sale",
  "description": "Test sale"
}

### Create Coin Transaction (invalid type)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1,
  "amount": 500,
  "type": "invalid_type"
}

### Create Coin Transaction (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1
}

### Delete Coin Transaction
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions/1

### Delete Coin Transaction (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/coin-transactions/99999
